# Streaming Functions Guidelines

## Line Length
Ensure that all lines do not exceed 79 characters, following the PEP 8 standard.

## Docstring Style
Use the Google docstring style for documentation.

## Utilize Core Utilities
Use `core_functions.py` utilities for logging and configuration.

## Cross-Platform Compatibility
Ensure compatibility across Windows, Linux, and Mac.

## Process Handling
Handle process creation with appropriate flags for each operating system.
